		</div>
		<p class="press-item-text medium-text">
			Wordoids are words that are made-up, but sound right.
			They follow the rules of phonetics, and if done properly, roll off the tongue.
			The need to have an online presence has increased the need for unique product and company names and has led to these wordoids.
			Yet, even with a made-up name, it’s important for the name to convey something about what the product or business actually is.
		</p>
		<div class="clear"></div>
	</div>
