		</div>
		<p class="press-item-text medium-text">
			This is a jewel of a web app.
			I may sound a little over zealous here, but it’s primarily due to the fact that I’ve been scouring my brain over recent weeks for a unique name for a small project I’m working on, but to no avail, I’m still struggling.
			Within about 10 minutes of using Wordoid, I’d found the perfect name and I’m delighted with it.
